    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，DiagnosticEngine是CTX上下文引擎，EMR_Sync就是我们的LLM网关。另外患者记录系统叫PatientRecords，实验室分析模块是LabAnalyzer。",
      "elements_involved": [
